    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fixtures and adapters, including ring-shaped, L-shaped, or T-shaped fittings, used in pipe and plumbing systems to connect pipe or tubing sections, to adapt piping to different sizes or shapes, to regulate flow, or for other purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
